        <h1 class="about-title history-title">40+ Years of Experience</h1>
        <p class="about-description history-description">Master Exteriors was created in 2000 by Erwin Coles, after spending nearly 30 years developing his skills as a carpenter.</p>
        <p class="about-description history-description">In 2009 Erwin began developing a tool that he initially created while working in Calgary years before. The tool—since called the Coles Clip—allowed a carpenter to install fiber cement board siding alone, nearly cutting labour costs in half for a small business like Master Exteriors. The Coles Clip that was eventually sold in hardware stores across PEI, as well as a store in Calgary. While the Coles Clip is no longer in production, those interested in learning more can contact Erwin directly at <a href="tel:1-902-629-0603">(902) 629-0603</a>.</p>
        <p class="about-description history-description">Master Exteriors has grown over the years to include Erwin's son Matt, roofing specialist Aram Bavandpour, and other workers depending on seasonal workload. We have taken on projects from a single window installation all the way up to the full exteriors of large houses and commercial buildings, working all around Eastern and Central Prince Edward Island.</p>
